code: public static int hash(String routing) {     final byte[] bytesToHash = new byte[routing.length() * 2].     for (int i = 0. i < routing.length(). ++i) {         final char c = routing.charAt(i).         final byte b1 = (byte) c, b2 = (byte) (c >>> 8).         // no information loss         assert ((b1 & 0xFF) | ((b2 & 0xFF) << 8)) == c.         bytesToHash[i * 2] = b1.         bytesToHash[i * 2 + 1] = b2.     }     return hash(bytesToHash, 0, bytesToHash.length). }
public static int hash(byte[] bytes, int offset, int length) {     return StringHelper.murmurhash3_x86_32(bytes, offset, length, 0). }
